{"tid":227891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］托迪退休","createTime":"2017-05-03T13:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T07:06:47.000Z","uid":64525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7d1e7c2a08965dc91f683f7a457346986c2ae7","tid":227891,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"It was the news we were all expecting to filter through sooner or later, this season, but that doesn't make it any easier to hear when it's made official.<br />\n<br />\nFrancesco Totti is to retire from football at the end of the season.<br />\n<br />\nThe news has just broken in Italy, courtesy of Roma's Sporting Director Monchi.<br />\n<br />\nThe Giallorossi Director said during a presentation this afternoon, &quot;In terms of Totti, I already knew that there was an agreement with the club that this would be his final year as a player, then he'd start as a director.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Francesco is Roma, I want to be as close to him as possible. I'd love to learn even one per cent of the huge amount that he knows.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nTotti's last match in a Roma shirt will come against Genoa at the Stadio Olimpico on 28th May. That means we've got just 25 days left of Francesco Totti as a professional footballer. Let's make the most of them while he's still lacing up his boots.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nddr終於坐正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edd3acc530b9eb5a13af6abcd0c11f243cc11e9","tid":227891,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"迪羅斯終於係羅馬隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c547d5be877afe79aa189fd05a7f76e6b9880c25","tid":227891,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪羅斯終於係羅馬隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n迪羅斯幾時退休到費羅倫斯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/n